      "patch": "@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@\n+created: 2025-12-05\n+title: Tenzir Changelog v0.11.0\n+intro: >-\n+  This release adds the `--co-author` option for crediting additional authors\n+\n+  (useful for AI-assisted development) and improves entry parsing to accept\n+\n+  the plural `components` key in frontmatter."
